
This package contains the ns2 implementation of VCP, a simple congestion control protocol that scales to high-bandwidth, long-delay networks. VCP is described in the following paper.

   Y. Xia, L. Subramanian, I. Stoica, and S. Kalyanaraman. One More Bit Is Enough. In Proceeings of ACM SIGCOMM'05, Philadelphia, PA, August 2005.

You can find the paper from any of the authors' home pages on the Internet, e.g., http://networks.ecse.rpi.edu/~xiay/vcp.html. More information, such as the technical report version of the paper, will be posted here.

If you have any questions, please feel free to contact me at xy12180@gmail.com.

-Yong

